Class PlayerProjectile

java.lang.Object
  java.util.Observable
      undecided.PlayerProjectile
All Implemented Interfaces:
Projectile
public class PlayerProjectile
extends java.util.Observable
implements Projectile

Author:
Team Exception The PlayerProjectile class is the bullets that PlayerTank will fire. It consists of a location speed in both the x and y direction and a projection of itself as a geometry class rectangle to control collisions.
See Also:
TankView, EnemyTank
